jobs.prompt:
You are working in Code&DBs/Workflow/surfaces/api/workflow_api.py.

Add two POST endpoints for saving manifests:

1. POST /api/manifests/save (inline handler in do_POST)
   Body: {id, name, description?, manifest (the full V2 JSON)}
   - If id exists: UPDATE app_manifests SET manifest = $1, name = $2, description = $3, updated_at = now()
   - If id doesn't exist: INSERT INTO app_manifests
   - Return: {saved: true, id, version}

2. POST /api/manifests/save-as
   Body: {name, description?, manifest, source_id?}
   - Generate new id from slugified name + 6-char uuid
   - INSERT INTO app_manifests
   - Return: {saved: true, id, name}

Follow the existing inline POST handler pattern (like /api/dispatch-job). Use self.subsystems.get_pg_conn(). Don't break existing endpoints.
